{"tid":986390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯兩架蘇-34戰機在日本海上空碰撞 俄搜救彈射逃生機員","createTime":"2019-01-18T11:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T12:02:53.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"385a9e5465cb6faf223406a14381847ad9ea2510","tid":986390,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"（中央社莫斯科18日綜合外電報導）俄羅斯2架蘇愷34（Su-34）戰鬥轟炸機今天在俄國遠東地區、日本海上空進行訓練飛行時擦撞，2架飛機墜落外海，機員彈射逃生。俄方正展開搜救行動。<br />\n<br />\n今日俄羅斯（RT）報導，俄國國防部證實，2架戰機於日本海上空空中「擦撞」。2架飛機墜毀於外海35公里處，搜救行動已展開。<br />\n<br />\n庫頁島海事救援中心表示，已出動1架An-12飛機和2架Mi-8直升機搜尋落水的逃生飛行員，另有船隻也已趕赴戰機墜毀海域。<br />\n<br />\n俄國軍方表示，意外發生時2機正進行訓練飛行，機上均未掛載任何武器。<br />\n<br />\n儘管天候惡劣，救援人員已定位到一艘充氣救生筏及其中一名飛官，軍方表示，飛官獲救前不斷向救援人員「打燈號」。<br />\n<br />\n俄國空軍於2010年代中期，啟用蘇愷34這款現代化中程戰鬥轟炸機，預計取代自1970年代至今仍服役的老舊蘇愷24轟炸機。蘇愷34能攜帶從精確制導炸彈到各類飛彈等多種武器。（譯者：陳亦偉/核稿：羅苑韶）1080118<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901180203.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201901180203.aspx&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=725a6822\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901180203.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"b5b073067bfe66ca693429412bc94860f9d6e831","tid":986390,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbc50b2619318439b9e8351f61c6169fe881a22","tid":986390,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"搞咩事，美軍之前炒完依家又輪到俄佬"},{"pid":"f0152deef88aa90a71f308565c3196442bc63882","tid":986390,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"係咪有單位試緊干擾系統"},{"pid":"5d71d228752bd2907c970ce6c78f11cf4eed05b9","tid":986390,"uid":50776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 屌你老母"},{"pid":"4b5c2cd821500666d79ca03eb644e8c161126968","tid":986390,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"又要威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84e9a1f0a9cb5d0ce761db1efdb45e798ec642a","tid":986390,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44b3f291e26e5add86fedcacf2854b81f8032065","tid":986390,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢d野耐唔耐會有好正常，好似某國乜都唔夠膽報咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9afa2fa186b18f88a18b6d21a62228b99a13dd","tid":986390,"uid":118079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"2104e538a6705874ad5e04649a57d74da71d036f","tid":986390,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"點解要飛咁近？ 又不係特技飛行。"},{"pid":"16daadc43c5dbe153df1e8a58fdb36642a62c83b","tid":986390,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"呢架野聽講話自帶廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}